  "text": "Circular No.664/55/2002-CX 25 th September, 2002 F.No.201/6/2002-CX.6(Pt.) Government of India Ministry of Finance and Company Affairs Department of Revenue Central Board of Excise and Customs CORRIGENDUM In Circular No.662/53/2002-CX, dated 17 th September, 2002: (1) the words, figures and brackets \"F.No.201/6/2001-CX.6(Pt.)\" appearing at the top of the opening page may be read as \"F.No.201/6/2002-CX.6(Pt.)\". (2) the words, figures and brackets \"(3) EOUs including EPZ units: EU\" appearing in sub paragraph (ii) of paragraph 5.3 may be treated as omitted. M.G.Thamizh Valavan Under Secretary to the Government of India -- 1 of 1 --",
